 on the connections between fossil studies in Europe and America, and on paleontology’s contributions to America’s developing national identity, The Legacy of the Mastodon is itself a fabulous discovery for every reader to treasure.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMammals, FossilzNorth AmericaxHistory. 0aMammothszNorth AmericaxHistoryy19th century. 0aMastodonszNorth AmericaxHistoryy18th century. 0aPaleontologyzNorth America. 0aPaleontologyzUnited States. 7aHISTORY / United States / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015184840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300151848423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300151848/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles